{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-24-1",
 "title": "A Cautious Contact on Pride 1",
 "summary": "Undercover as Mege Vauki, the NRI agent Bazil McKenzie lands the Triton on the Griffon Alliance station Pride 1 hoping to meet General Patricio Rey for intelligence on the Death Star, only to find Rey absent. He instead encounters Thayra Delmund, a guarded Griffon operative who deflects his cryptic probing until the two exchange verified identity chips and she accepts his New Republic Intelligence credentials. Retiring to the secluded Galaxy Rose tavern, Bazil recounts witnessing the Death Star obliterate Gastus and pleads for any information the Griffons hold. Thayra admits her people know little more than rumor, having seemingly lost contact with their own assets, and the two agree to share whatever either side uncovers, parting with mutual wariness and grim resolve. A trader named Khirsah, recognized from a holoterm, briefly crosses Bazil's path during the encounter.",
